							<title xml:lang="he">וכוח על נצחיות התורה</title>
							<note>
								<p>An account of public religious debate held in the Convent of Jesuits in Ferrara in April 1617 between the anonymous author (perhaps Azriel Petahyah Aletino) and a Jesuit priest, Alphonso Caracciola, by order of the papal legate, Cardinal Orazio Spinola. </p>
